Chutih lai chuan Thlarau Thianghlimin min rawn pawl leh ta a. Khawvel intlansiakna kawnga tumruh taka tlân ka nih laiin, ka hmaah hian khawvel ropuina leh mawina te, zirna kawng tinreng leh ka nupui fanau leh ka nu leh pa leh ka chhungte hi an lo lang ta thut mai a. Thlarau Thianghlim ngei mai chuan ka thinlung chhungah hian, “Hengte zawng zawng hi i dam chhan a ni lo,” a rawn ti ta a. Chu veleh chuan keiin, “Lalpa, engnge ni ka damchhan ni ta ang le?” tiin ka zawt ta a. “Kei, thihna hneha tholeha hi i dam chhan ka ni; kei mi dam chhan chhung zawng chuan i tân ka nung tih i hre zel ang,” tih hi fiah êm êm hian a rawn ri ta a.
